README

Keyboard Controls
A = Move Left
D = Move Right
Move Mouse =  choose inital ball direction and secondary ball if chosen

Mouse Controls
Move Mouse = Movement
A = initial ball direciton left and second ball left if chosen
D= initial ball direciton right and second ball right if chosen

Default Direciton = Left
Default Second Ball Position = Left

